{"tid":1877942,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"查頓辛祖今夏離隊　曼聯準備12億搶購","createTime":"2020-02-13T09:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T13:22:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"72abe6887aec03279f2984efda3d39c122b43d76","tid":1877942,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"曼聯冬窗期間錯失簽入挪威新人王艾寧夏蘭特，畀多蒙特捷足先登，真係喊都無謂，不過希望在明天，德國傳媒突然爆料，多蒙特嘅英格蘭新人王查頓辛祖將於今夏離隊，下個目的地正係曼聯，值得魔迷期待。<br />\n<br />\n德國《天空體育》報道，3月滿20歲嘅查頓辛祖決定今夏離開多蒙特，佢喺蜜蜂兵團效力3季，至今上陣84場入29球，其中今季29場入15球，係時候重返英超。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯一直希望簽入呢位新人王，另外車路士亦對佢有興趣，不過車路士近日有新目標，打算簽入阿積士摩洛哥翼鋒薛耶治，查頓辛祖就留番畀曼聯。消息指曼聯今夏繼續擴軍，收購查頓辛祖嘅預算達到1.2億鎊(約12億港元)，可謂志在必得。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200213060137735-0213_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20200213060137735-0213_00882_001%26whichpage%3D1&d=2Od897eOL%2Byk6rGVR7zebRdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=3197b31e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200213060137735-0213_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"675361be4c49ed64ab34ce1f22074f68f0074cee","tid":1877942,"uid":53029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:57:09.000Z","msg":"港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5215546cd20e544dca2b1dad105ad46d89f789ec","tid":1877942,"uid":4156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"去曼聯即刻變垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d21ceddccba7134237e3e076cd997a8b0f395c","tid":1877942,"uid":179007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:42:09.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n佢個個都話要<br />\n有邊個出名少少獌聯無傳過架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 